@startuml sequence_create_variant
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Sequence — Create Tailored Resume Variant

actor "Job Seeker" as User
participant "content/base/" as Base
participant "content/notes/" as Notes
participant "content/tailored/" as Tailored

User -> Base : Select base file\n(focused or full)
Base --> User : Returns base Markdown

User -> Notes : Open notes file\nfor target role
Notes --> User : Returns role snapshot,\nbullets, keywords

User -> Tailored : Create <company>-<role>.md\nwith YAML front matter\n(source_base, company, role)
User -> Tailored : Customize bullets and\nkeywords from notes

Tailored --> User : Tailored variant ready\nfor document generation

@enduml
